Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.98,0:00:09.54,Default,Beta,0,0,0,,寫不出來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.45,0:00:11.48,Default,Beta,0,0,0,,阿爾法大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.73,0:00:15.11,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,怎麼了？《暗影大人戰記》的執筆有進展了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.11,0:00:16.17,Default,Beta,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.93,0:00:18.71,Default,Beta,0,0,0,,沒有什麼進展
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.71,0:00:23.54,Default,Beta,0,0,0,,看到那副無與倫比的英姿 不湧出創作欲望是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.85,0:00:24.59,Default,Beta,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.59,0:00:25.56,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,但是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.56,0:00:28.98,Default,Beta,0,0,0,,寫完過了一會自己重新讀過後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.98,0:00:31.16,Default,Beta,0,0,0,,總覺得不太對
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.58,0:00:34.97,Default,Beta,0,0,0,,真正的 真正的暗影大人的厲害之處
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.97,0:00:38.19,Default,Beta,0,0,0,,我沒能將其表達得淋漓盡致
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.87,0:00:44.18,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,是啊… 以你現在的文章確實還沒夠到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.64,0:00:45.43,Default,Beta,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.78,0:00:49.84,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,即便如此 也不可能放棄追逐他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.84,0:00:50.66,Default,Beta,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.16,0:00:52.90,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,是吧？ 貝塔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:54.50,Default,Beta,0,0,0,,是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.85,0:00:57.16,Default,Beta,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.16,0:00:59.14,Default,Beta,0,0,0,,心情稍微輕鬆了一點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:00.24,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.71,0:01:04.85,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,你的作品 暗影庭園的女孩們都很期待的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:06.93,Default,Beta,0,0,0,,我會加油的！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.61,0:01:09.83,Default,Beta,0,0,0,,對了 有件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.83,0:01:15.05,Default,Beta,0,0,0,,想問問和暗影大人認識最久的阿爾法大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:15.91,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.27,0:01:20.57,Default,Beta,0,0,0,,方才的戰鬥 暗影大人被那群傢伙拷問時
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.57,0:01:22.41,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,求饒話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.86,0:01:26.85,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,雖然不知道他的舉動有什麼樣的意圖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.11,0:01:28.64,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,但真是逼真的演技哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.47,0:01:31.41,Default,Beta,0,0,0,,是什麼樣的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.14,0:01:32.77,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,欸！？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.77,0:01:35.93,Default,Beta,0,0,0,,能否請您重現一次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.67,0:01:37.76,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,我來？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.76,0:01:41.18,Default,Beta,0,0,0,,是啊 真好是阿爾法大人目擊到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.73,0:01:50.82,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,呀…還請…還請饒我一條性命啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.93,0:01:53.56,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,大概是這個感覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.56,0:01:54.70,Default,Beta,0,0,0,,原來如此！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.56,0:01:57.00,Default,Beta,0,0,0,,這個感覺嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.00,0:01:59.23,Default,Alpha,0,0,0,,不對 應該是這個感覺！
